{"tid":1095371,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"坪石邨老婦上吊 昏迷送院","createTime":"2019-04-07T03:46:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-07T03:57:33.000Z","uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fcf9ea66916d8ba3d42ed7d641199814a20f205e","tid":1095371,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T03:46:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190407/large/1554604837_c4e1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190407%2Flarge%2F1554604837_c4e1.jpg&h=4ef4fa82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早上9時許，一名年約80歲老婦，於牛池灣坪石邨紅石樓一單位上吊自殺，女兒發現報警求助，警方及救護員接報後到場，將昏迷老婦送院搶救，警方正調查事件。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=bZmkWp0iUYBi2b5pBzw%2FEZmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=42f6cf40\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.openup.hk</a>"},{"pid":"8b1bf3adc1b8d1f8c9f6578c066c67c3f65903ae","tid":1095371,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T03:57:33.000Z","msg":"邊個話抵死嘅話我屌佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}